{"tid":2067515,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"滙豐內部備忘錄重申支持港區國安法","createTime":"2020-06-17T05:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T06:10:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78748a80cd35659941ae937f26c5062e60409d28","tid":2067515,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"滙豐內部備忘錄重申支持港區國安法<br />\n17.06.2020 13:08<br />\n滙豐控股(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGzpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=31e84784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)亞太區行政總裁王冬勝支持「港區國安法」引起美英政府批評，彭博社報道，滙豐環球銀行及資本市場聯席主管向員工發內部備忘錄，重申滙控支持港區國安法的立場。在「一國兩制」的原則下，尊重和支持所有穩定香港社會秩序、振興經濟的法律。備忘錄指，雖然客戶近日的每次討論幾乎都談及香港，但滙豐在亞洲和西方經濟體之間的橋樑角色，可紓緩客戶的擔憂，強調中西方將繼續擁有深厚的經貿關係，香港將繼續擔當重要的渠道角色。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧批評滙控是向北京「表忠」，但未能贏得北京的尊重。"},{"pid":"5b97227bd877c995f4314612d3b20ba8ad2cd156","tid":2067515,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"HSBC <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6b4a694994c4e67131be79826f649960411c0a","tid":2067515,"uid":128923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b97227bd877c995f4314612d3b20ba8ad2cd156","tid":2067515,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"HSBC <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"呢排英國硬撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3000a0a6e9c77bd4a2663da128215c458c177e90","tid":2067515,"uid":2471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"滙豐前線好多黃"},{"pid":"d53ec6452fa6001637bbd777cfd303d12833d834","tid":2067515,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"